title: Guest column: Syracuse football team faces 'Reality-Check Day' in game with No. 25 Pitt
text: Guest column: Syracuse football team faces 'Reality-Check Day' in game with No. 25 Pitt 2015 Syracuse football first half Defense has been a problem of late for the youthful Syracuse University football team. Better tackling . . . better scheming . . . better coverage . . . it'll all be paramount if SU is to upset the 25th-ranked Pittsburgh Panthers in the Carrier Dome on Saturday afternoon. Or so suggests guest columnist (and former Orange running back) Roger Praetorius in his weekly essay below. (Stephen D. Cannerelli/The Post Standard 2015)
